Smoky Chipotle Black Bean Burger with Avocado Lime Crema

$12.99
550 kcal
Difficulty: 40%

Allergens:

SoyDairy

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-FreeHigh Protein

Tags:

GourmetComfort FoodPlant-Based

Description

A hearty, smoky black bean burger topped with creamy avocado lime sauce for a burst of flavor in every bite!

Ingredients

  • Black beans: 1 can (15 oz)
  • Chipotle peppers in adobo: 2
  • Garlic: 2 cloves, minced
  • Onion: 1 small, diced
  • Cilantro: 1/4 cup, chopped
  • Cornmeal: 1/2 cup
  • Egg: 1
  • Salt: 1 tsp
  • Black pepper: 1/2 tsp
  • Avocado: 1
  • Lime juice: 2 tbsp
  • Greek yogurt: 1/4 cup
  • Olive oil: 1 tbsp
  • Whole wheat burger buns: 4
